之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=XjQgjJGG3Jmbsj%2FlSM8MSG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9d180b64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"cd6f4ec74140fda05c6d69a86ae139a46952b122","tid":886950,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce9df4e0749ec475414986e5c339827bb8fc913c","tid":886950,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"239b0dc47a819d8b7efc1ca7a6caacb88efb66a7","tid":886950,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10da3f569848ab0e8d67cd201ff3dd8105085f45","tid":886950,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"恭喜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://sdl-stickershop.line.naver.jp/stickershop/v1/sticker/11088113/android/sticker.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fsdl-stickershop.line.naver.jp%2Fstickershop%2Fv1%2Fsticker%2F11088113%2Fandroid%2Fsticker.png&h=e43b3446&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:32:00.000Z","msg":"屌 好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  摩牙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"冇 屎就有得你食"},{"pid":"f95b387638393de1f2dea665008100f57a92b5ee","tid":886950,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95dda8f2cc6138f3870fad483aae95fa8424582c","tid":