m/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=XjQgjJGG3Jmbsj%2FlSM8MSG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9d180b64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"37efe38d995dc6280320e3e3194a458d661715ca","tid":886950,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e60cd7048471295344c87b3b5f026940d93888a","tid":886950,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eca320a21f8838ed937846bf0ef5a42d07e0fd3a","tid":886950,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d69f6c7aa7385d13fc25e7176ad9389ee69d20","tid":886950,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"無了無了 乜都無了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"乜"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"急尿 但廁所有人"},{"pid":"8bff265ffd8b3ee2fcf6fc68cbd88a0aac23ea30","tid":886950,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37efe38d995dc6280320e3e3194a458d661715ca","tid":886950,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e60cd7048471295344c87b3b5f026940d93888a","tid":886950,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eca320a21f8838ed937846bf0ef5a42d07e0fd3a","tid":886950,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"無了無了 乜都無了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"乜"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"急尿 但廁所有人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，